        <h1>Help: actions</h1>
        <table style="width: 100%;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
            <col style="width: 65.491%;" />
            <col style="width: 34.509%;" />
            <tr valign="top">
                <td style="width: 65.491%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;border-right-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;" width="65.491%">
                    <p class="TitoloInterno">
                        <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />Action</p>
                    <div class="MCDropDown MCDropDown_Open dropDown"><span class="MCDropDownHead dropDownHead"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="MCDropDownHotSpot dropDownHotspot MCDropDownHotSpot_">Creating a daily calendar (valid every day)
                                </a></span>
                        <div class="MCDropDownBody dropDownBody">
                            <div>
                                <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                                    <li class="p" value="1">
                                        <p>Select the <span style="font-weight: bold;">Daily calendar</span></p>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="p" value="2">
                                        <p>Set the band (start time&lt;end time) when it is on</p>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="p" value="3">
                                        <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/dbllistbox/arrowdx_on.png" style="border: none;float: none;border-style: none;width: 54px;height: 19px;" width="54" height="19" border="0" /> to add the time interval</p>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="p" value="4">
                                        <p>Repeat to add as many time intervals as needed</p>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="p" value="5">
                                        <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/add_on.png" style="border: none;float: none;border-style: none;width: 24px;height: 24px;" width="24" height="24" border="0" /> to add the calendar</p>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="MCDropDown MCDropDown_Open dropDown"><span class="MCDropDownHead dropDownHead"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="MCDropDownHotSpot dropDownHotspot MCDropDownHotSpot_">Creating a weekly calendar (valid every week)
                                </a></span>
                        <div class="MCDropDownBody dropDownBody">
                            <div>
                                <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                                    <li class="p" value="1">
                                        <p>Select the <span style="font-weight: bold;">Weekly calendar</span></p>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="p" value="2">
                                        <p>Select the days of the week and the band (start time &lt; end time) when it is on</p>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="p" value="3">
                                        <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/dbllistbox/arrowdx_on.png" style="border: none;float: none;border-style: none;width: 54px;height: 19px;" width="54" height="19" border="0" /> to add the time interval</p>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="p" value="4">
                                        <p>Repeat to add as many time intervals as needed</p>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="p" value="5">
                                        <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/add_on.png" style="border: none;float: none;border-style: none;width: 24px;height: 24px;" width="24" height="24" border="0" /> to add the calendar</p>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 34.509%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;border-right-style: none;border-top-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;" width="34.509%">
                    <p>This section is more operative: it lists all the possible actions in the described application window.</p>
                    <p>Sentences written in blue are <span style="font-weight: bold;">drop-down links</span>. </p>
                    <p><span style="font-weight: bold;">Click on the sentence</span> to expand the page and display hidden information.</p>
                </td>
